message.body: Hi guys I think I'm going to stick around norristown tomorrow afternoon , are you guys cool with me driving and then you taking the r100 back?
Yo are you down to leave soonish?
I just got to breakfast but yeah. Also do you need your car in norristown or does it make more sense for me to drive and you to take the train home?
I need my car in norristown, if you want your car too we could always drive separately...
What time do you want to meet, closer to 8 or 8:10?
Alright I'm ready, meet me by the stop sign?
